<div id="review_2823444514" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2823444514" />
    <a title="Joann" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/28272513-joann"><img alt="Joann" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2823444514?book_show_action=true">May 22, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joann" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joann" href="/user/show/28272513-joann">Joann</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2823444514" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10259243271537415234">A very thoughtful book connecting gardening and poetry, poetry and gardening, both of which Mr. Kunitz excelled at. His writing is beautiful. It is easy to picture his gardens which he loves so much. I am sad he is no longer here to create beautiful gardens and poetry and to write about them.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


