<span id="freeTextContainer16998012500741284887">A friend recently read a poem to our group. In in, she included that the Wildest Braid lay open upon the desk When I asked about the book, she urged me to read it. It is lovely. I have sent the library copy back, purchased myself a copy to keep, and four more for friends. I will read this book for years to come.</span>

          </span>
