              <span id="reviewTextContainer5089008" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15365612038583194310">I read this autobiographical poetry book while on vacation and it was a perfect(re)introduction to Cape Cod. Poet Kunitz lived in Provincetown, CC and loved the place. He passed away last year at the age of 100 after spending most all his life writing and editing. Beautiful book!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


