<li class='cover' id='bookCover_50358133'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50358133-homeland-elegies"><img alt="Homeland Elegies" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1584627596l/50358133._SX98_.jpg" />
