<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer4793800921624128135">Stanley Jasspon Kunitz was an American poet. He was appointed Poet Laureate Consultant in Poetry to the Library of Congress twice, first in 1974 and then again in 2000.</span>

